Interviews with food and wine notables such as author John Alonge, Chef Bernard Guillas (pictured), Rocker turned winemaker Mick Fleetwood, and Robert Mondavi of the famed winemaking family round out the variety of people and subjects Taste of Wine TV and The Wine Smarties encompasses in the weekly round-up of news, information and education.]]></description>
